FlexMoneyAssignment Yoga Admission Form

Registration Page
User need to fill their basic details, based on validations
and click on Pay button

Database
After successful payment, user data will be stored in the database.
Database store all information after payment.
Important Assumptions made
1) Email ID will be the primary key.
2)By clicking on Payment button, payment will be successful.
3)The validation is done for the registration page only.

Step to run the project
Clone the repo.
Intall node, express, mongoDB.
Install dependencies mention in package.json file.
Run mongoDB.
Run command "node server.js"
